<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.7">
<l>ulavu tiraikkaṭaṟ paḷḷikoṇṭu vantu ṉaṭiyēṉ maṉampu kuntavap</l>
<l>pulava puṇṇiya ṉēpukun tāyaip pōkaloṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>nilavu malarppuṉṉai nāḻal nīḻaltaṇ ṭāmarai malariṉ micaimali</l>
<l>alavaṉ kaṇpaṭukku maṇiyāli yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will not consent to the departure of you who entered [me], pure one,</l>
<l rend="indent">that sage who, coming [after] sleeping in the tossing sea waves,</l>
<l>Entered the mind of your servant, me,</l>
<l>Lord of lovely Āli where a huge crab rests on top of a fresh lotus blossom</l>
<l>In the shade of the cassia and shining, blooming laurel [trees].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
